        </tr>

        <tr>
          <td style="padding:40px 60px; font-size:16px; line-height:1.75;">
            <p>尊敬的 <strong>{{.Cid}}</strong>:</p>
            <p>您好,</p>
            <p>您的管制权限已更新：</p>

            <div style="margin:25px 0; padding:20px; border-radius:12px; background-color:#f0fff8; border:1px solid #bdf5c1;">
